# Mock Data Layer

## Key 命名规范
```
ecommerce:{module}:{datatype}
```

示例：
- `ecommerce:settings:params`
- `ecommerce:logistics:vendors`
- `ecommerce:quality:inbound`

## Storage 封装
```javascript
import { get, set, remove, clearByPrefix } from '../utils/storage';

// 读取
const data = get('ecommerce:settings:params');

// 写入（自动 schemaVersion）
set('ecommerce:settings:params', newData);

// 清空模块
clearByPrefix('ecommerce:settings:');
```

## Mock 文件模板
```javascript
// src/mock/{module}/{datatype}.js
import { get, set } from '../../utils/storage';

const STORAGE_KEY = 'ecommerce:{module}:{datatype}';

const defaultData = [
    { id: 1, name: '示例', status: 'enabled', createdAt: '2024-01-15' }
];

export default function getMockXxxList() {
    const stored = get(STORAGE_KEY);
    if (stored) return stored;
    set(STORAGE_KEY, defaultData);
    return defaultData;
}
```

## Schema Version
存储结构：`{ schemaVersion: 1, data: <any> }`
版本不符 → 返回 null → service 用 mock 回填
